# This file is intentionally empty.
#
# Single source of truth is the monorepo root `.env` (one file shared by the
# NestJS backend AND both admin SPAs). The admin Vite config reads it and
# shovels VITE_*-prefixed keys into process.env at build/dev time.
#
# To override a value just for this SPA, create `.env.local` here (gitignored)
# with the VITE_* keys you want — Vite reads .env.local with higher priority
# than the root .env walk.
